# User Stories â€“ Web shop E -Commerce Application

## US-01: User Login
As a registered customer  
I want to log in using valid credentials  
So that I can access my account and place orders.

Acceptance Criteria:
- User should be able to log in with valid username and password
- Error message should be displayed for invalid credentials
- Session should be maintained after successful login

---

## US-02: Product Search
As a customer  
I want to search products using keywords  
So that I can quickly find required items.

Acceptance Criteria:
- Relevant products should be displayed for valid search
- No results message should be shown for invalid keywords

---

## US-03: Add Product to Cart
As a customer  
I want to add products to cart  
So that I can purchase them later.

Acceptance Criteria:
- Product should be added to cart successfully
- Cart quantity should update correctly

---

## US-04: Checkout Process
As a customer  
I want to checkout selected products  
So that I can place an order.

Acceptance Criteria:
- User should be able to proceed to checkout
- Order confirmation should be displayed after successful checkout

